text.text: Head down-right and talk to young lady outside BIG WAVE.
Interact with teenage boy, Advert Ship, old lady, and young man.
Pulse in by wavehole near your house.
Talk to Hertz. Press B to not read any tutorials.
Folder Edit. Equip Image Eye Mega Weapon.
Go back towards Advert Ship. Skip tutorial. 3 Forced Encounters.
After the tutorial, pulse out. Head back towards Advert Ship.
Talk to man in suit, head over towards Luna's house. Cutscene.
Pulse in, head to roof of Luna's house. Grab propellor. Pulse out.
Talk to man in suit again.
Head home, TalkToMom.
Leave house, pulse in.
Enter house, interact with TV to enter TV ES.
Head to left side of ES, talk to Hertz. Pulse out twice.
Enter house, TalkToMom, go to sleep.
Exit house, pulse in. Go back inside house and enter your room.
Grab HPMem10 BMW.
Exit house, walk to Mailbox and enter Mailbox ES.
Grab HPMem10 BMW on left side of ES.
Pulse out twice, walk to and interact with Bus Station sign.
Pulse in to left of elevator. Enter Street Sign ES.
Grab Cloaker BMW at bottom of ES.
Pulse out twice, enter elevator.
Talk to teenage girl, young man, Sonia sign, man in suit, and old man (numbered circles).
Head to IFL Tower
Approach IFL Tower. After cutscene, try to enter the Tower.
Head back towards Shopping Plaza. Cutscene.
Head down and talk to man in suit.
Talk to young man.
Talk to young lady.
Pulse in, enter Mega Display ES. Grab 450z BMW on right side of ES.
Exit ES, check out young lady's Star Carrier.
Pulse out, talk to young man.
Talk to Bud. Enter Shopping Plaza.
Head up elevator. Talk to Mr. Boreal, but don't read any tutorials.
Head up elevator, approach movie theater.
Exit Theater, talk to left lady at counter.
Exit Theater, talk to man in front of elevator.
Pulse in at wavehole near Theater entrance.
Enter Security Cam ES. Grab 550z BMW at top of ES. Exit ES.
Talk to merchant Hertz to buy HPMem20 for 1000z.
Take warp to second floor.
Grab HPMem10.
Take warp to first floor.
Interact with counter, pulse out.
Take elevators down to first floor. Attempt to leave.
Take elevators up to third floor. Talk to left lady at counter.
Take elevators down to first floor. In front of electric ghosts, open Menu > Item > Matter Wave > Vacuum.
Exit Shopping Plaza.
Head to IFL Tower. Approach the Tower.
Pulse in on right side of Tower.
Head down-left, take warp up to Wave Road.
Head up-left into cutscene.
Follow path up IFL Tower, avoiding ghosts along your way.
Take warp 2, realize path is broken.
Grab HPMem10. Potential folder edit. Use a Cloaker.
Interact with ghosts for forced fight.
Go back to where broken path was, and head to IFL Tower 2.
Continue following the path. There are 2 ghosts attacking people you need to interact with to fight.
Fight Dark Phantom.
